701550f-b.text:
(1)
Olmstead Ave., north from Ellis Ave., showing, at the S.W. corner of Newbold Ave., the Olmstead Avenue Presbyterian Church. In the background appears a portion of the elevated structure of the I.R.T. Pelham Bay Park subway line on Westchester Ave.

July 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr

(2)
The same, at a later date.

May 10, 1938.

P. L. Sperr.

(3)
An exclusive view of the church, as seen from Newbold Ave.

May 10, 1938.

P. L. Sperr.
